content: <metadata>   <idinfo>     <citation>       <citeinfo>         <origin>City and County of Denver Surveyor's Office</origin>         <title>Right-of-Way Ordinance Name Change</title>         <geoform>vector digital data</geoform>       </citeinfo>     </citation>     <descript>       <abstract>This layer displays ordinances and resolutions relating to City and County right-of-way. Included are name changes. These actions are not depicted on City Surveyor's office linens, and are dated 1996 to the present. ROW ordinances older than 1996 but missing from the linens are also digitized in this layer.</abstract>       <purpose>Acquisition and disposal actions relating to City and County right-of-way, mostly dating from 1996 to the present.</purpose>       <supplinf>These data are continuously updated.</supplinf>     </descript>     <status>       <progress>In work</progress>       <update>Continually</update>     </status>     <spdom>       <bounding>         <westbc>-105.053047</westbc>         <eastbc>-104.734751</eastbc>         <northbc>39.791024</northbc>         <southbc>39.624266</southbc>       </bounding>     </spdom>     <keywords>       <theme>         <themekt>None</themekt>         <themekey>engineering</themekey>         <themekey>survey</themekey>       </theme>       <theme>         <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Categories</themekt>         <themekey>boundaries</themekey>         <themekey>planningCadastre</themekey>       </theme>       <place>         <placekt>None</placekt>         <placekey>Denver</placekey>         <placekey>Denver County</placekey>         <placekey>Colorado</placekey>         <placekey>USA</placekey>       </place>     </keywords>     <accconst>None</accconst>     <useconst>ACCESS CONSTRAINTS:   None.
